title: Mott_The_Hoople-Argent_KBFH_1974_(Quad)
description:
Here is a special gift to you Mott The Hoople 96 Decibel Freaks out there,
on both sides of the Atlantic, and beyond, not sure how long I can seed this
so I'd appreciate if a few people could keep this alive, I do have another
very interesting one to post to, and would like to, though low disk space
and it being hot enough to melt a C.P.U. without Air Conditioning makes it
hard to get these things going.
 And thanks to all the members of Mott, that are here with us and gone, for
making History, and letting us be a part of it. 
Enjoy ! This is my special gift especially to you Limey's on the other
side of the ocean !
